; TLD zone fixture for recursive E2E tests (task #472).
; Authoritative for test., delegates example.test. to 127.0.0.3.
$ORIGIN test.
$TTL 3600
@   IN SOA  ns1 hostmaster ( 1 3600 900 604800 300 )
@   IN NS   ns1
ns1 IN A    127.0.0.2
example.test. IN NS ns1.example.test.
ns1.example.test. IN A 127.0.0.3
